             was indicted for <rs id="t18000219-41-off245" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18000219-41-off245" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18000219-41-off245" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18000219-41-cd246" type="crimeDate">22d of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000219-41-off245 t18000219-41-cd246"></join>, seven pair of women's shoes, value 28s. and two pair of girl's shoes, value 6s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18000219-41-victim395" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Morgan
                  <interp inst="t18000219-41-victim395" type="surname" value="Morgan"></interp>
